data.description: This Move-In Ready, well-maintained home exudes timeless elegance with gleaming hardwood floors gracing every room. It showcases newer roof, siding, windows, electrical system, and a modern kitchen and bathroom. The oversized detached garage, currently leased month-to-month, provides an additional income stream, making it a valuable asset. The open kitchen features an eat-in area, perfect for cozy meals and gatherings, and it overlooks a spacious backyard, ideal for outdoor entertainment. With 3 bedrooms (and the potential to easily add a 4th), and 1.5 updated baths, it strikes the perfect balance between modern upgrades and classic charm. Freshly painted throughout, this home is a blank canvas for your personal style. Located just a short walk from Borough Rustic Park and its state-stocked Trout stream, it's the epitome of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today to see it for yourself, and be sure to inquire about our 2-1 buy down option that can save you hundreds of dollars.
